data.description: Welcome to this stunning Cragmoor gem! Recently refreshed with new luxury vinyl flooring on the main level and new deck paint and stain, this spacious home offers a large lot ideal for families and pet lovers. Enjoy breathtaking views of Palmer Park from the back deck and kitchen. Stay comfortable with a cozy fireplace for winter evenings. The living room features a charming bay window and a gas fireplace, seamlessly flowing into the adjacent dining area. The dining area opens onto the deck and kitchen, making entertaining a breeze. Conveniently, the attached garage provides direct access to the kitchen and a convenient half bathroom. Upstairs, discover three bedrooms, including a master bedroom with direct access to a generous full bathroom. Both west-facing bedrooms offer captivating views of Pikes Peak. The walkout basement boasts its own 3/4 bathroom, laundry room, a spacious family room, and a versatile "bonus area." This space is perfect for a playroom, guest suite, or a family/game room combination. Whether you seek your own dream home or a savvy investment property, this residence is a true find. Situated in a prime location with easy access to UCCS, University Village Colorado, medical facilities, hospitals, and more, this home offers an exceptional lifestyle.
